title: 09/11: Waiver Wire (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
While there doesn't appear to be any player you should break the bank on, we do have a lot of interest in Phillip Lindsay, George Kittle, Quincy Enunwa, Kenny Golladay, Eric Ebron and many more. We give you our top priorities (2:15) and talk FAAB (9:05) at the top of show before taking a closer look later ... IdiotMoron Move of the Week (14:30) and a recap of CHI-GB (22:22), LAR-OAK (26:22) and NYJ-DET (28:28) ... Many more Waiver Wire names at QB (34:41) including Tyrod Taylor and Case Keenum, RB (42:15) including Austin Ekeler and Aaron Jones, WR (46:04) including too many names to list here, TE (53:06) including Jonnu Smith and Ben Watson, K and DST (58:00) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
